Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.94,0:01:11.31,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,The first semester midterms have ended...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:11.80,0:01:14.21,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:14.21,0:01:15.51,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.51,0:01:17.59,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to Sadako's review session!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:17.87,0:01:20.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much, Sadako!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:24.56,0:01:28.25,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,...and it's almost time for the school festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:28.69,0:01:30.80,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:30.80,0:01:31.97,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Constipation? Diuresis?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.97,0:01:33.52,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's so creepy!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:33.52,0:01:37.35,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly that junior Sadako Kuronuma grows them.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:37.35,0:01:38.34,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.34,0:01:40.81,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh her! I've seen her before!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.81,0:01:44.57,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,There have been stories about her curses since freshmen year!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.57,0:01:45.45,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:49.04,0:01:54.78,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,The theme for this year's school festival is Fantasy!
