Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.37,0:02:05.27,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can participate too.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:07.89,0:02:10.90,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever's fine, just hurry up and pick.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.90,0:02:12.40,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me! I have one!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.90,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,What about "Sadako's Black Magic Café"? {aw yeah time for some snooty accents}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.49,0:02:17.69,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Black magic?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.69,0:02:20.70,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's famous among the freshmen too.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.70,0:02:23.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We can use those weird herbs she grows and make tea.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.16,0:02:28.54,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,We could make an "Ask Sadako" booth!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.54,0:02:30.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But make it more like a fortune-teller's tent!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.56,0:02:35.05,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,She's doing well for herself.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:35.05,0:02:35.67,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's a great idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.59,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's take a vote!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:46.64,Chalkboards,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord2\fs30\an7\3c&H3D5446&\pos(99,528)}Class Exhibit\NSadako's Black Magic Cafe: 26\NHaunted House: 7\NCostume Parade\NMidnight Monster Parade
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.17,0:02:48.85,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:49.36,0:02:51.03,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That's Vap Ca. {http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Houttuynia_cordata#Medicinal_use}{made it cap'd 'cause that's how it is on the wiki page}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.56,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, there's a Vap Ca tea, isn't there?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.56,0:02:55.58,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What about this one?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.78,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,That's perilla. {http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perilla#Japan}{only cap}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.02,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're growing perilla?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:59.02,0:03:01.66,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be helpful to have some on hand.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.62,0:03:05.58,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Here come the guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.73,0:03:08.20,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.20,0:03:09.60,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.60,0:03:12.66,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako's growing a bunch of medicinal herbs!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:39.32,0:03:43.46,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think we could use perilla in the café?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:44.55,0:03:46.01,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.66,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.26,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,We could make tea with it.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.26,0:03:55.43,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. As long as you steep it in hot water, you can make tea with just about anything.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.01,0:03:58.63,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you use rosemary.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.91,0:04:00.38,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Rosemary?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:00.38,0:04:07.87,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to him, but I didn't know what to say.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.96,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's my imagination,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.96,0:04:13.71,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,but it feels like we've drifted even further apart now.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.14,0:04:22.49,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the one who's drifting away from him?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.93,0:04:35.86,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Sawako is trying to talk to him but \NKazehaya's just been so difficult lately...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.46,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:38.96,0:04:42.80,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably the most different from her.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.32,0:04:48.10,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. I'm screwed if I don't fix this.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.06,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I could get Ryu to—
