Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.10,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,going with you this Sunday, right? {more like she's going with him, but his name needs to come first}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:55.25,0:04:56.40,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,To the wedding?
