Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.83,0:05:01.77,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're going together in his dad's car.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.77,0:05:02.78,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,When are you guys leaving?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.88,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Around 7.
