Dialogue: 5,0:05:39.03,0:05:43.55,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.39,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yano-chin!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.23,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.23,0:05:49.53,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.53,0:05:51.67,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,I had a doll like this once.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.98,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what style you're trying to do, foundation is crucial.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.05,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yano-chin…
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.20,0:06:05.15,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming over so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.84,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. I got a good laugh out of it too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.19,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Chizu?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.31,0:06:17.57,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's not all about making your eyes look big or whatever…
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.57,0:06:18.66,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Can I try?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.44,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Great.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.44,0:06:24.78,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,The almond shape of your eyes is what makes them beautiful.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:24.78,0:06:25.36,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.69,0:06:30.82,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,You have to leverage that to show off your beauty.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.41,0:06:36.58,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Today's an important day for you too.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.00,0:06:43.09,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,And afterwards, let's highlight your eyes in a pale pink to soften the look.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:43.09,0:06:44.19,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Does it look okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.47,0:06:47.05,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. Like a completely different person!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.02,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.60,0:06:59.77,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.56,0:07:06.93,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get in the car!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.35,0:07:09.56,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you later!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.68,0:07:35.64,Default,Toru,0000,0000,0000,,Chi!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.64,0:07:38.39,Default,Toru,0000,0000,0000,,You and I will be even closer now. {we'll never grow apart}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.86,0:07:40.91,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean it?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.91,0:07:42.77,Default,Toru,0000,0000,0000,,I mean it!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.46,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Toru, Haruka,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.46,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,congratulations.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.48,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.57,0:08:40.90,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,That was a beautiful wedding, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.33,0:08:42.28,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.27,0:08:48.29,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, it's almost time for your summer tournament, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.29,0:08:50.67,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's right after the school festival.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.03,0:08:53.64,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck! You guys better win this time!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.64,0:08:55.22,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.17,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.61,0:08:58.78,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:01.46,0:09:02.67,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,There's something, isn't there?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.53,0:09:23.05,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:23.51,0:09:24.50,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.13,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why not??
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.13,0:09:27.75,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want to.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.75,0:09:31.28,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?! You just have to tell him what he wants to hear!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.28,0:09:35.91,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You can say that he totally understands Sawako, 100%!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.91,0:09:40.33,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think that works.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.33,0:09:41.39,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to say it.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.14,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:44.14,0:09:45.27,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:50.00,0:09:53.61,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask him what's wrong though.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.78,0:10:02.09,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,But not for your sake. It's 'cause I'm worried about him too.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:02.91,0:10:07.08,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,And that doesn't mean I'm going to tell you anything if he tells me.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:08.36,0:10:10.17,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for this.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.17,0:10:13.09,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,What? Ryu!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.97,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Shota, you're not going to the cafeteria?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.83,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You go on ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.78,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna drop off this toolbox first then head over.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.29,0:10:34.73,Default,Joe,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Kazehaya!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:35.02,0:10:35.99,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.46,0:10:41.82,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited for the Black Magic Café!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:41.82,0:10:44.33,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,There's the Ask Sawako fortune-telling booth too.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.77,0:10:48.43,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.43,0:10:51.00,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't actually have any supernatural powers…
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.00,0:10:54.34,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Will I really be able to help people with their problems?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.45,0:10:59.45,Default,Ayane,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it. Just tell them what you see.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.45,0:11:02.84,Default,Chizu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're really good at that!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.79,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.61,0:11:27.19,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I could make tea with a blend of perilla and Thunberg's geranium…
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.19,0:11:29.08,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.13,0:11:31.58,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.07,0:11:35.81,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a talk with you. Are you free now?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:41.61,0:11:45.28,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I am an amazing man~ {needs sugoi particles and effects}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.28,0:11:48.46,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I am an amazing man~ {hardsubbed, ofc.}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:48.46,0:11:52.18,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not letting you sleep tonight either! {and a bouncing head}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:59.37,0:12:00.55,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Shota!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.20,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.71,0:12:04.76,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.24,0:12:18.30,Italics,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep what Chizuru said in mind.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.15,0:12:27.82,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, did you decide to confront her or not?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.61,0:12:30.66,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Your soup…
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.66,0:12:32.65,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that come from?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.65,0:12:35.23,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering what's wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.41,0:12:46.35,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know how I should treat her anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.63,0:12:50.65,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I've always acted however I liked around her.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.71,0:12:54.25,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I did that for her sake.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.92,0:12:58.36,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Some of the things I did probably bothered her.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.36,0:13:02.90,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,And when I think of that, I just don't know what to do anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.31,0:13:08.73,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Then I think I could just ask her…
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.18,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.16,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she'd actually say something's bothering her?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.18,0:13:16.78,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,Probably not.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.78,0:13:17.65,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.90,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, looky here. It's Shota!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.20,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Sitting all the way over here, calmly eating his lunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.66,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong with that?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:28.66,0:13:32.46,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:33.86,0:13:36.00,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Your lover's cheating on you at the moment!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:36.66,0:13:38.75,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,With Kent Miura.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.53,0:13:47.86,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.26,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,That's not cheating and we're not together.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.55,0:13:51.97,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.97,0:13:54.27,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Then that means…
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.25,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You were rejected?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.31,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You were rejected!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.07,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I was not!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.65,0:14:11.91,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Then you haven't even confessed to her yet, is that it?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.86,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,You should just tell her how you feel!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.58,0:14:21.73,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Sing out your love to her under the majestic sun.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.73,0:14:28.90,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Work up your small, insect-like courage and confess your love from the top of the jungle gym! {i love this guy!!!}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.80,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this guy know so much?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.26,Default,Ryu,0000,0000,0000,,That was delicious.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.26,0:14:36.10,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Time for lunch.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.10,0:14:38.37,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're already done, Ryu?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.60,0:14:44.19,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when Kuronuma probably knows nothing at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:44.86,0:14:49.09,Italics,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Or wait. It's possible that she does know but just finds it annoying.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.67,0:14:58.16,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't understand her.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.91,0:15:03.98,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,So what? Of course you don't.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.28,0:15:08.53,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.18,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.60,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you say they were?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.64,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.64,0:15:19.87,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kuronuma?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:20.63,0:15:23.94,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,She's by that weird garden—
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.94,0:15:25.20,Default,Pin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.72,0:15:35.03,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you're fitting in really well. I'm so glad, Sadako.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.24,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Fitting in? Me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.83,0:15:48.80,Kaleido,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(340,340)\be1\pos(151,294)}Seeing \N\Nher life \N\Nflash \N\Nbefore \N\Nher eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:48.80,Box,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(340,340)\pos(153,296)}A
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.59,0:15:46.73,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this what fitting in is like?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.63,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I've only ever seen it in my dreams!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.45,0:15:52.76,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just notice?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.07,0:15:57.52,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer an outcast.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.14,0:16:03.38,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,See, even without Kazehaya's help, you're totally fine!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.37,0:16:08.72,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.58,0:16:14.60,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Or did you always want to be an outcast so that Kazehaya would help you?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:19.24,0:16:20.49,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 5,0:16:21.91,0:16:24.17,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been my goal...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.21,0:16:28.04,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Can I play too?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.61,0:16:31.28,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,...to be able to fit in with everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:31.62,0:16:33.33,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.95,0:16:36.35,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's something I've always longed for.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.45,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 5,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.39,Default,Kazehaya,0000,0000,0000,,Kuronuma.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.77,0:16:45.65,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's always treated me so normally,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:46.91,0:16:50.15,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot all about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.15,0:16:54.40,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,He only cares about you because you look so depressed all the time! {you don't do anything else but look depressed and he cares about you}
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.31,0:17:00.40,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,He just cared about me because I seemed depressed.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.09,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:03.09,0:17:07.75,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy but I'm also… shocked.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:09.11,0:17:13.77,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I always looked up to that part of Kazehaya.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.33,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,It's an easy mistake to make.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.31,0:17:23.47,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,With Kazehaya always paying special attention to you and all.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.29,0:17:27.25,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Does he know?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.25,0:17:29.00,Italics,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! He really is a psychic!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:29.00,0:17:34.88,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kazehaya didn't mean to do any harm.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.75,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,He's just kind of insensitive I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:37.21,0:17:40.41,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.16,0:17:46.27,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Kazehaya's always fair and kind and friendly, no matter who he's dealing with!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.27,0:17:49.63,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,He's always greeted even me with a smile!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.43,0:17:55.38,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,When I told him how I felt, he believed me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.91,0:18:04.02,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,He's the first person I could talk to without feeling like there was a wall between us.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.58,0:18:10.64,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he's always like that that I fell in love with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.59,0:18:18.56,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, that wasn't enough anymore.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.31,0:18:22.16,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe how greedy I was becoming.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.12,0:18:27.37,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,I interpreted things wrong…
Dialogue: 5,0:18:28.52,0:18:31.50,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You knew you were wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:33.11,0:18:38.01,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, stop! It's hard to admit stuff like this, even to myself.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.01,0:18:40.77,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.77,0:18:43.68,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,That insensitive jerk!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.06,0:18:51.90,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it'd be a good idea to avoid Kazehaya from now on?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.75,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,For both of your sakes!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.75,0:18:56.82,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,Both our sakes?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:56.82,0:19:01.93,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You should live your own life, enjoy your youth!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:01.93,0:19:05.02,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,And Kazehaya's "mission" would be completed so he could—
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.66,0:19:13.46,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako, Kazehaya has someone he likes. {I HATE YOUUUUUUU}
Dialogue: 5,0:19:15.46,0:19:19.56,Default,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,He's already rejected me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.08,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to tell you,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.63,0:19:30.71,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,but now don't you think you can leave him alone?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:30.71,0:19:33.63,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to be a bother to him, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.07,0:19:38.19,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,You should start over.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.27,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Have other crushes!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.27,0:19:43.57,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Experience a lot of fun—
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.56,0:19:48.70,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Sadako?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.20,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,There was someone.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.31,0:19:54.68,Default,Sawako,0000,0000,0000,,There really was someone.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.09,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! {DO YOU FEEL BAD NOW ><}
