Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.08,0:20:31.45,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, it's okay!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.20,0:20:34.78,Default,Kent,0000,0000,0000,,Have some confidence in yourself!
